race.description: Sole Refrigeration & Air Conditioning F&M Hcp
race.comment: Wide open again. SHANGHAI VENTURE (7) is much better than last start on a very much rain-affected day at Geelong. Best form stacks right up to this level and gets chance to atone. SELF SERVE (6) is another below best latest. Was going along well before tackling a Class 1 over the border and didn't finish it off. Runner-up previous two starts and drawn for a soft run here. DRONE ATTACK (1) ran a nice race fresh to place when running on hard. Fitter again and looks a leading chance despite the wide draw. PURE RAIN (8) is a mare back from a long spell. Has placed 3/4 fresh and was a recent trial winner. Among the chances if presented on song. SHE IS ALL MAGIC (9) was disappointing last time when safely held at the picnics. Was a winner the start prior with Gatt aboard and he returns to the saddle this time. Can bounce back.
